{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"explicitNotify"},{"type":"text","text":", then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#canonical-parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/InitiallyUnownedSignalName\/notify"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/initiallyunownedsignalname\/notify"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/InitiallyUnownedSignalName"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Case","title":"InitiallyUnownedSignalName.notify","externalID":"s:10GLibObject26InitiallyUnownedSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/InitiallyUnownedSignalName/notify":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/initiallyunownedsignalname\/notify","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/InitiallyUnownedSignalName\/notify","abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"title":"InitiallyUnownedSignalName.notify","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"#canonical-parameter-names":{"title":"canonical parameter names","identifier":"#canonical-parameter-names","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"canonical parameter names"}],"url":"#canonical-parameter-names","type":"link"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","title":"GLibObject","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/InitiallyUnownedSignalName":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"InitiallyUnownedSignalName","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"InitiallyUnownedSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"InitiallyUnownedSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/initiallyunownedsignalname","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/InitiallyUnownedSignalName"}}}